title: RAISED BY WOLVES Episode 1-3 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: Was debating whether to do breakdowns for this one. Here's hoping this doesn't turn into Alien Covenant! 👽
Everyone gangsta till mother starts flying
Did anyone notice how Father has THE BEST DAD JOKES????
Am I the only one that watched three episodes more than three times 🤪 L O V E  I T

The show is hands down amazing!  In fact this show has the makings of a potential masterpiece!  I have only seen the first three episodes, but it feels like watching three movies!  The cgi, cinematography and story are so well executed as to be quite frankly on par with modern big budget films!  The writing, acting and compelling story in the first three episodes is quite literally amazing.  Think Game of Thrones but for science-fiction!  9/10 stars!
description:
In this video we take a deep dive and breakdown episodes 1, 2, and 3 of HBO Max's latest sci-fi show directed by Ridley Scott, RAISED BY WOLVES. Review, recap, and easter eggs!
